title: Volleyball Cheers for Cheerleaders
text:
We are the (school mascot) and you know what we got.What do you got?WE got a team thats hotter than hot!How hot is hot?Bumps, sets and spiking too,Wooo Woo Woo WooSo hit the ball like the rest of us do! 
Ace: Stomp stomp clap stomp stomp clap stomp stomp stomp stomp stomp stomp ACEOther team hits ball out: 1, 2, SeeyaYour team calls ball out and it's out:G-double o-d-e-y-e Goodeye GoodeyeSpike: 1, 2 kaboom-boomBlock: Captian yells BRICK everyone else yells wall! 
Bump, Set, Hit, SpikeThat's the way we like to fight! 
We're Gonna Bump, Set And Spike It'Cuz That's The Way We Like ItWe're Gonna Win!(clap)(clap) 
Just like the other oneAce ace ace ace ace! 
Additional All-Purpose Cheers 
Who are you yelling for?The Demons [insert your team's name]Stand up and yell once moreThe DemonsLouder now, let's hear it forThe Demons!
